Add the NGR 200 Xbox 360 to the list of recognized controllers.

Signed-off-by: Nilton Perim Neto <niltonperimneto@gmail.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250608060517.14967-1-niltonperimneto@gmail.com
